1
00:00:00,150 --> 00:00:03,480
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#483951">Class Monitor</font></b></font></font>

2
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:09,780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#39303f">Rules</font></b></font></font>

3
00:00:09,610 --> 00:00:11,740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font color="#1a1212"><font size="16"><b>Class Monitor</b></font></font></font>

4
00:00:24,260 --> 00:00:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A class monitor's morning starts early.</i></font>

5
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading out on patrol now.</font>

6
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:42,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if Poem-san is still sleeping.</font>

7
00:00:44,530 --> 00:00:46,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She does sleep well.</font>

8
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As you know,</i></font>

9
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:51,360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font size="20"><b>Kohinata's
Home</b></font></font>

10
00:00:47,280 --> 00:00:51,360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an2}<font size="20"><font color="#000000"><b>Sakuradaimon's
Home</b></font></font></font>

11
00:00:47,480 --> 00:00:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sakuradaimon-kun's home 
is really close to Poem-chan's.</i></font>

12
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poem-san?</font>

13
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:09,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

14
00:01:11,810 --> 00:01:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

15
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry, wrong person.</font>

16
00:01:15,450 --> 00:01:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you a friend of my older sister?</font>

17
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

18
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, the only one 
with such an odd name</font>

19
00:01:22,350 --> 00:01:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would be my older sister.</font>

20
00:01:24,630 --> 00:01:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Po-chan!</font>

21
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:30,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Po-chan!</font>

22
00:01:30,610 --> 00:01:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come down for breakfast!</font>

23
00:01:33,370 --> 00:01:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you <i>are</i> off today, 
you can't just sleep forever.</font>

24
00:01:43,170 --> 00:01:48,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="20"><font color="#000000">A Day Off With the <font color="#0fbde5">Klutz</font></font></font></b></font></font>

25
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's only 8:30?</font>

26
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Po-chan!</font>

27
00:01:54,290 --> 00:01:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

28
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:03,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you go wash up before eating?</font>

29
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I'm fine. I'll do it later.</font>

30
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't blame me then.</font>

31
00:02:09,540 --> 00:02:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mama warned you.</font>

32
00:02:12,050 --> 00:02:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Confusing.</font>

33
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you go jogging 
every morning, Lyric-san?</font>

34
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great.</font>

35
00:02:18,530 --> 00:02:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wearing a skirt and showing off thick legs
like my sister does would be embarrassing.</font>

36
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true.</font>

37
00:02:23,660 --> 00:02:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poem-san has nice legs.</font>

38
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell are you doing here, Togo?!</font>

39
00:02:38,610 --> 00:02:40,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}She really is a funny person.</font>

40
00:02:41,990 --> 00:02:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poem-san!</font>

41
00:02:43,170 --> 00:02:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

42
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyri! Did <i>you</i> let him in?!</font>

43
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look at me. We were 
chatting out front when Mama...</font>

44
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be Sakuradaimon-kun!</font>

45
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? Come in, come in.</font>

46
00:02:54,970 --> 00:02:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have breakfast with us!</font>

47
00:02:57,620 --> 00:02:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama! Jeez!</font>

48
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

49
00:03:00,270 --> 00:03:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a second, Poem-san!</font>

50
00:03:01,490 --> 00:03:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't blame your mother!</font>

51
00:03:04,460 --> 00:03:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was originally my fault 
for coming into your home</font>

52
00:03:07,650 --> 00:03:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so early in the morning.</font>

53
00:03:11,100 --> 00:03:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we have grown close, 
that was careless of me.</font>

54
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

55
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take my leave at once.</font>

56
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, no...</font>

57
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could I ever let myself be so rude?!</font>

58
00:03:24,370 --> 00:03:25,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please just give me a moment!</font>

59
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll leave once I've finished this!</font>

60
00:03:33,570 --> 00:03:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't you think shoveling it 
down like that is rude too?</font>

61
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You're leaving, Sakuradaimon-san?</font>

62
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, but you see, Lyric-chan....</font>

63
00:03:45,650 --> 00:03:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyri! Why, you!</font>

64
00:03:47,250 --> 00:03:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? Let him stay.</font>

65
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:52,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, why don't you go get changed first?</font>

66
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gonna stay in pajamas forever?</font>

67
00:03:54,450 --> 00:03:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakuradaimon-san, you can 
take your time eating, okay?</font>

68
00:03:58,330 --> 00:04:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'm sorry.</font>

69
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's so difficult.</i></font>

70
00:04:06,210 --> 00:04:07,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So?</font>

71
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just want to make sure for now,</font>

72
00:04:10,050 --> 00:04:13,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you're not going out, right? You two?</font>

73
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:16,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Going... Wha?! Huh?! No way!</font>

74
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! We're not dating.</font>

75
00:04:18,710 --> 00:04:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

76
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For one thing, illicit relationships 
are prohibited in our school's rules.</font>

77
00:04:22,730 --> 00:04:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! Really?!</font>

78
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay, so that's the stage they're at.</i></font>

79
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you interested in dating 
at all, Sakuradaimon-san?</font>

80
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Lyri!</font>

81
00:04:30,770 --> 00:04:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are doing asking 
such personal things?!</font>

82
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hardly.</font>

83
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you panicking for? 
We're just chatting.</font>

84
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't say I'm not 
interested in romance.</font>

85
00:04:38,690 --> 00:04:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though a student's main duty is to study.</font>

86
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:44,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir, that's really a line 
only smart people can use.</font>

87
00:04:44,930 --> 00:04:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're not <i>uninterested</i>?</font>

88
00:04:46,610 --> 00:04:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good for you, Big Sis.</font>

89
00:04:48,380 --> 00:04:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's your problem today?!</font>

90
00:04:49,610 --> 00:04:51,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what's your type?</font>

91
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My type, you ask?</font>

92
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Lyric!</font>

93
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Type... My type, huh?</font>

94
00:04:58,490 --> 00:05:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't thought about it before.</font>

95
00:05:00,700 --> 00:05:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of woman do I view fondly?</font>

96
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm.</font>

97
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Diligent, well-mannered, honest... Hmm?</font>

98
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:12,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, those are certainly traits 
that I desire for myself,</font>

99
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}but it feels wrong to say 
I seek them in women.</font>

100
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are proper to a fault, huh?</font>

101
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wait, judging women by 
my preferences seems wrong too...</font>

102
00:05:17,210 --> 00:05:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're funny.</font>

103
00:05:18,590 --> 00:05:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how about my older sister?</font>

104
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's neither diligent
 nor well-mannered,</font>

105
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but she can be surprisingly cute.</font>

106
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey!</font>

107
00:05:25,620 --> 00:05:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Hold on!</font>

108
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that.</font>

109
00:05:28,140 --> 00:05:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poem-san is a cute, kindhearted, 
and all-around wonderful woman.</font>

110
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You hold on too!</font>

111
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Ow!</font>

112
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What was that?</font>

113
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you two should go out already.</font>

114
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you two 
still not dating yet? Scary.</font>

115
00:05:38,860 --> 00:05:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyri!</font>

116
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're getting too carried away! 
I'll get mad!</font>

117
00:05:42,570 --> 00:05:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I just don't get it.</font>

118
00:05:44,290 --> 00:05:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was only giving you 
an extra push, Big Sis.</font>

119
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey you two, 
you shouldn't fight each other.</font>

120
00:05:48,990 --> 00:05:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay, Sakuradaimon-kun!</font>

121
00:05:53,650 --> 00:05:59,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These two are actually 
very close siblings!</font>

122
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, here's a snack. Eat up!</font>

123
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today we're having Po-chan and 
Lyri-chan's favorites, PreChure Pancakes!</font>

124
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama!</font>

125
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times do I have to say it?!</font>

126
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not into things like this anymore!</font>

127
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is wonderfully well done, ma'am!</font>

128
00:06:15,570 --> 00:06:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Sakuradaimon-kun!</font>

129
00:06:17,770 --> 00:06:19,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, this takes me back!</font>

130
00:06:19,970 --> 00:06:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To that day when the three of us 
went to the PreChure movie together.</font>

131
00:06:29,910 --> 00:06:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">PreChure Heartthrobbing Love Cherry Splash!</font>

132
00:06:54,330 --> 00:06:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're finished.</font>

133
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Foolish PreChures.</font>

134
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place will be your grave!</font>

135
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:13,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sis, what do we do?! 
The PreChures are going to lose!</font>

136
00:07:13,180 --> 00:07:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't give up, Lyri! Look!</font>

137
00:07:16,580 --> 00:07:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All you good kids!</font>

138
00:07:18,050 --> 00:07:22,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need you to help by sharing some 
of your light energy with the PreChures!</font>

139
00:07:22,570 --> 00:07:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, everyone!</font>

140
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grab your PreChure Wands!</font>

141
00:07:26,410 --> 00:07:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, let's go!</font>

142
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Lyri!</font>

143
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Wave your wands!</i></font>

144
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have the magic light 
they gave us when we entered, right?</font>

145
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Everyone, lend us your power!</i></font>

146
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wave it to support them!</font>

147
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:35,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Thank you!</i></font>

148
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}S-So cute!</i></font>

149
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drive off those evil villains 
with the power of light!</font>

150
00:07:37,940 --> 00:07:40,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My daughters are so cute!</i></font>

151
00:07:48,570 --> 00:07:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

152
00:07:53,990 --> 00:07:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it! PreChure!</font>

153
00:07:58,010 --> 00:08:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can do it! PreChure!</i></font>

154
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Drive off those evil villains 
with the power of light!</i></font>

155
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Arial"><b>{\an8}<font size="20"><font color="#7a23c8">Evil Villains</font></font></b></font></font>

156
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, Mama! Go somewhere else!</font>

157
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:12,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? No fun. I want to chat too!</font>

158
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:19,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="16"><b><font color="#4df841">Evil Villain</font></b></font></font>

159
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:19,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="16"><b><font color="#cd00d7">Evil Villain</font></b></font></font>

160
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:19,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="16"><b><font color="#2cfff0">You Can Do It, PreChure</font></b></font></font>

161
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:19,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="16"><b><font color="#f8ff16">Klutzy Class Monitor</font></b></font></font>

162
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with that, 
Poem-san, Lyric-san!</font>

163
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead, ma'am! 
Please sit here with us.</font>

164
00:08:18,230 --> 00:08:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said!</font>

165
00:08:20,340 --> 00:08:23,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so kind, Sakuradaimon-kun!</font>

166
00:08:23,230 --> 00:08:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama, jeez!</font>

167
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my, I didn't realize 
I had stayed so long.</font>

168
00:08:29,590 --> 00:08:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the food.</font>

169
00:08:31,090 --> 00:08:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you said it.</font>

170
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:37,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would've thought I'd spend 
the whole day off with you at home?</font>

171
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come back again, Sakuradaimon-kun!</font>

172
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shoo! Shoo!</font>

173
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't hung out at a friend's house
since elementary school.</font>

174
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for letting me 
have a really fun time.</font>

175
00:08:48,050 --> 00:08:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well, uh...</font>

176
00:08:51,660 --> 00:08:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry it was so noisy.</font>

177
00:08:54,210 --> 00:08:58,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad Pa—my father was out.</font>

178
00:08:58,160 --> 00:09:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That old man's 
the most annoying one of all.</font>

179
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was nice and lively.</font>

180
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, well, Lyri said all those things...</font>

181
00:09:08,690 --> 00:09:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

182
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a little sister 
around Lyric-san's age too.</font>

183
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:18,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Girls around their age 
love to talk about that stuff.</font>

184
00:09:18,970 --> 00:09:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't take it seriously.</font>

185
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

186
00:09:26,210 --> 00:09:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Right! That's right!</font>

187
00:09:29,530 --> 00:09:31,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, excuse me.</font>

188
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah!</font>

189
00:09:32,610 --> 00:09:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful on your way home! 
Even though it's close!</font>

190
00:09:41,220 --> 00:09:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could have taken it 
a <i>bit</i> more seriously.</font>

191
00:09:44,210 --> 00:09:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dummy.</font>

192
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?!</font>

193
00:09:49,540 --> 00:09:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you say something?</font>

194
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing!</font>

195
00:09:58,580 --> 00:09:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go home, go home!</font>

196
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you tomorrow!</font>

197
00:10:01,170 --> 00:10:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. See you later.</font>

198
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sis.</font>

199
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one's going to 
be difficult, you know?</font>

200
00:10:10,010 --> 00:10:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's all kinds of off.</font>

201
00:10:12,010 --> 00:10:15,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font color="#8d0b38">Rules</font></b></font></font>

202
00:10:12,450 --> 00:10:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dating's against school rules, right?</font>

203
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He might end up just
leading you on until graduation.</font>

204
00:10:20,090 --> 00:10:23,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He seems like the kind of guy 
who's a walking embodiment of the rules.</font>

205
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:22,270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="18"><b><font color="#4b317e">Guy Walking Around 
in a Shirt That Reads <font color="#1a1919">"Rules"</font></font></b></font></font>

206
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:24,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lyri.</font>

207
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had plenty of fun teasing me today,</font>

208
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you're prepared for 
the consequences, right?!</font>

209
00:10:32,530 --> 00:10:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Calm down.</font>

210
00:10:34,910 --> 00:10:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it for your sake!</font>

211
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

212
00:10:38,490 --> 00:10:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make excuses, Lyri!</font>

213
00:10:41,650 --> 00:10:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Wait!</font>

214
00:10:43,090 --> 00:10:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop running!</font>

215
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Lyri!</font>

216
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did she mean by 
take it more seriously?</font>

217
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:51,050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font color="#e0d6e1">Totally Heard Her</font></font>

218
00:10:55,970 --> 00:11:00,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="20">{\an5}m 0 0 l 115.5 0 l 115.5 108 l 0 108</font></font>

219
00:10:55,970 --> 00:11:00,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="20"><font color="#000000">{\an5}The <font face="Arial"><b><font color="#0cc0e9"><font size="20">Klutzy
<font color="#000000"></font></font></font></b>Class Monitor<font size="12"> and
<font size="16">the <font size="20"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#dc3a95">Girl <font color="#ffffff"><font size="12">with
<font color="#000000"></font></font></font></font></b><font size="16">the <font size="20"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#dc3a95">Short Skirt</font></b></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

220
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Klutz and the Skirt!</font>

221
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:05,940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="20">{\an5}m 0 0 l 115.5 0 l 115.5 108 l 0 108</font></font>

222
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:05,940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="20"><font color="#000000">{\an5}The <font face="Arial"><b><font color="#0cc0e9"><font size="20">Klutzy
<font color="#000000"></font></font></font></b>Class Monitor<font size="12"> and
<font size="16">the <font size="20"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#dc3a95">Girl <font color="#ffffff"><font size="12">with
<font color="#000000"></font></font></font></font></b><font size="16">the <font size="20"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#dc3a95">Short Skirt</font></b></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

223
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Klutz and the Skirt!</font>

224
00:11:08,310 --> 00:11:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So good!</font>

225
00:11:12,130 --> 00:11:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If Togo spots me in a place
 like this again...</font>

226
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:17,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Dining on your way 
to and from school is prohibited!"</font>

227
00:11:17,190 --> 00:11:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The first time is a warning!"</font>

228
00:11:18,450 --> 00:11:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The second time, 
it's a reflection essay!"</font>

229
00:11:21,210 --> 00:11:23,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what he'd likely say.</font>

230
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with this? Jeez.</font>

231
00:11:32,130 --> 00:11:37,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an3}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="20"><font color="#000000">The <font color="#10bce8">Klutz <font color="#000000">Gets Plunged Into Battle on the Streets</font></font></font></font></b></font></font>

232
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hmm, what's the best thing I can get 
to show my thanks to Poem-san's family?</font>

233
00:11:40,220 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><b><font color="#f37913">Power Strip</font></b></font>

234
00:11:40,220 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="16"><b><font color="#040504">Trust It With Them All!</font></b></font></font>

235
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This looks like something 
the whole family could use!</font>

236
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. I'll get this one!</font>

237
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we don't need it!</font>

238
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poem-san?!</font>

239
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing in a place like this?</font>

240
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could ask you that!</font>

241
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank us? For having you 
over the other day?</font>

242
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

243
00:11:57,360 --> 00:12:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You treated me to breakfast 
and shared pancakes with me too.</font>

244
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I felt like I needed 
to do something in return—</font>

245
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't need that! 
<i>Especially</i> not a power strip!</font>

246
00:12:10,270 --> 00:12:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama just did that on her own anyways!</font>

247
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you bring a gift, Mama will just get 
fired up and bake cookies or something!</font>

248
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she returned my thanks 
with more thanks...</font>

249
00:12:20,770 --> 00:12:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'd have to thank her yet again!</font>

250
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I'm saying you don't need to!</font>

251
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sentiment is more than enough
 for things like that!</font>

252
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

253
00:12:35,250 --> 00:12:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then allow me to visit one more time
to show my appreciation.</font>

254
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure.</font>

255
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about today?</font>

256
00:12:43,330 --> 00:12:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's far too sudden!</font>

257
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True. I'm sorry.</font>

258
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It <i>is</i> already late in the day.</font>

259
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's only part of it.</font>

260
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:56,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, what are you doing 
while on patrol?</font>

261
00:12:56,130 --> 00:12:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You went on and on about how 
we can't buy food on the way home,</font>

262
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet now you're shopping?</font>

263
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that a violation of the rules too?</font>

264
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I went home first.</font>

265
00:13:06,770 --> 00:13:08,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm not on my way home anymore.</font>

266
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of cheap logic is that?!</font>

267
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The trip home from school 
lasts until you reach your home.</font>

268
00:13:14,310 --> 00:13:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't talk like it's a field trip!</font>

269
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if you already went home, 
why are you still wearing your armband?!</font>

270
00:13:18,690 --> 00:13:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I'm pretty sure I was 
wearing it on our day off too.</font>

271
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. You were!</font>

272
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, why?!</font>

273
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:29,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I'm a class monitor, of course!</font>

274
00:13:29,330 --> 00:13:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not an answer!</font>

275
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More importantly, I still haven't heard 
your answer to my previous question.</font>

276
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here, Poem-san?</font>

277
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:41,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

278
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She then manages to fool him.</i></font>

279
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your family is full of nice,
 cheerful people.</font>

280
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see how you grew up 
to be so kind and honest.</font>

281
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up.</font>

282
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those pancakes were amazing too.</font>

283
00:13:59,730 --> 00:14:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a wonderfully perfected PreChure!</font>

284
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

285
00:14:03,490 --> 00:14:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say any more and I'll punch you!</font>

286
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

287
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At any rate, you all showed me 
wonderful hospitality.</font>

288
00:14:10,190 --> 00:14:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to meet your father next time.</font>

289
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My papa...</font>

290
00:14:14,610 --> 00:14:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father is rather annoying, 
so it's seriously better if you don't meet him.</font>

291
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Annoying?</font>

292
00:14:20,770 --> 00:14:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First off, he'll probably punch you 
just for being a man in our home.</font>

293
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

294
00:14:26,890 --> 00:14:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll give you a preemptive punch 
before hearing you out.</font>

295
00:14:30,020 --> 00:14:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He never listens to what people say.</font>

296
00:14:32,390 --> 00:14:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also...</font>

297
00:14:39,770 --> 00:14:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

298
00:14:47,860 --> 00:14:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My name is Kohinata Rhyme.</i></font>

299
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm 37.</i></font>

300
00:14:53,180 --> 00:14:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just finished work for today,</i></font>

301
00:14:56,100 --> 00:15:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I'm hurrying home 
to my beloved family.</i></font>

302
00:15:03,650 --> 00:15:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Believe it or not,</i></font>

303
00:15:05,860 --> 00:15:09,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was quite a handful when I was young.</i></font>

304
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But now, I'm very dedicated to my family.</i></font>

305
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:20,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm seen as a diligent, devoted father.</i></font>

306
00:15:21,180 --> 00:15:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I had my first child at 21,</i></font>

307
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and she's now a 16-year-old 
high schooler.</i></font>

308
00:15:26,210 --> 00:15:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My youngest daughter is entering 
her third year of middle school.</i></font>

309
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mama, today's my bento box day.</font>

310
00:15:32,690 --> 00:15:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, okay. Hold on a minute!</font>

311
00:15:35,330 --> 00:15:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's my gym uniform?</font>

312
00:15:38,460 --> 00:15:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They hardly talk to me anymore, 
like most girls their age.</i></font>

313
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

314
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're coming shopping too, Papa?</font>

315
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to.</font>

316
00:15:48,430 --> 00:15:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get some rest. Aren't you tired?</font>

317
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no point in you being there.</font>

318
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can just go with Mama,</font>

319
00:15:54,430 --> 00:15:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you don't need to come.</font>

320
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But on the few occasions they do,</i></font>

321
00:15:59,010 --> 00:16:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can feel their appreciation 
for me in their words.</i></font>

322
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm surprised such good daughters 
managed to come from me.</i></font>

323
00:16:12,660 --> 00:16:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shouldn't be saying this, 
but my life has all been smooth sailing.</i></font>

324
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have a shred of discontent, 
whether in my career or in my family life.</i></font>

325
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However...</i></font>

326
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There is one exception.</i></font>

327
00:16:26,050 --> 00:16:27,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

328
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their music's too loud.</font>

329
00:16:28,970 --> 00:16:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, they're forming a cypher.</font>

330
00:16:31,330 --> 00:16:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A cypher?</font>

331
00:16:32,630 --> 00:16:37,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's when multiple people get together
 for some freestyle rapping.</font>

332
00:16:37,730 --> 00:16:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's only one exception
that stirs my heart.</i></font>

333
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I was young, 
back before I met my wife,</i></font>

334
00:16:47,590 --> 00:16:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it was the one thing 
I was passionate about.</i></font>

335
00:16:53,410 --> 00:16:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Uh...</font>

336
00:16:55,590 --> 00:16:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're dumb! And ugly!</font>

337
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The lowest of the low.</i></font>

338
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dissing physical looks is the same 
as declaring you have nothing else to say.</i></font>

339
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would...</i></font>

340
00:17:13,260 --> 00:17:14,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, no!</i></font>

341
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I retired from the street 
over 17 years ago.</i></font>

342
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What could I even accomplish 
by joining those young people?</i></font>

343
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My beloved family is 
anxiously awaiting my return.</i></font>

344
00:17:28,650 --> 00:17:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shouldn't be loitering around here.</i></font>

345
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! What's your problem?!</font>

346
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you all think 
you're doing in this space</font>

347
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">frequented by people 
in front of the station?!</font>

348
00:17:41,340 --> 00:17:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a class monitor, 
I can't overlook this!</font>

349
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wha?! Who's that?!</i></font>

350
00:17:47,050 --> 00:17:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Judging from his outfit, he clearly 
has nothing to do with that group!</i></font>

351
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he barging in?!</i></font>

352
00:17:54,190 --> 00:17:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On that cypher?!</i></font>

353
00:17:56,050 --> 00:17:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I recognize all of you.</font>

354
00:17:58,430 --> 00:18:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all students 
at our school, aren't you?!</font>

355
00:18:02,170 --> 00:18:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Sakuradaimon, the class monitor.</font>

356
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:09,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, the guy who nags people
 at the school gate every morning!</font>

357
00:18:09,690 --> 00:18:12,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dare to just waltz right in here?!</font>

358
00:18:12,450 --> 00:18:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, get him!</font>

359
00:18:14,100 --> 00:18:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to humiliate 
this haughty class monitor!</font>

360
00:18:17,590 --> 00:18:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hey, yo!</i></font>

361
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why the hell are you here?!</i></font>

362
00:18:20,620 --> 00:18:23,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You rule-abiding teacher's pet.</i></font>

363
00:18:23,410 --> 00:18:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Class spies like you can go on, get.</i></font>

364
00:18:25,860 --> 00:18:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We've had enough of 
your brown-nosing act.</i></font>

365
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're just the man's little mutt,</i></font>

366
00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so you sure ain't gonna
 find friends near.</i></font>

367
00:18:33,970 --> 00:18:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're full-on tough thugs</i></font>

368
00:18:35,650 --> 00:18:37,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like a rabid pack of hyenas</i></font>

369
00:18:37,970 --> 00:18:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So tuck your tail, and beat it!
 Scram! See ya!</i></font>

370
00:18:42,530 --> 00:18:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's plain for anyone to see 
that he's not versed in rap battles,</i></font>

371
00:18:46,790 --> 00:18:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and they're planning 
to publicly execute him!</i></font>

372
00:18:49,810 --> 00:18:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How cowardly!</i></font>

373
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hyenas?</font>

374
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:54,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

375
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you made a metaphor 
with animals and our positions.</font>

376
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The thing about hyenas is 
they are nocturnal.</i></font>

377
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:05,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we're still students
so here's a kernel.</i></font>

378
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Early to bed, early to rise.
Don't make your parents worry.</i></font>

379
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Correct that biorhythm 
in a real fast hurry!</i></font>

380
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:13,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shouting and making a fuss at the station?
I don't get this kind of sensation.</i></font>

381
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It only serves to lower 
our school's stellar reputation.</i></font>

382
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:18,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The cost to your grades 
is as clear as an equation!</i></font>

383
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now go and return 
to your place of habitation.</i></font>

384
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He hit him with a response?!</i></font>

385
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What was that?!</i></font>

386
00:19:31,290 --> 00:19:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was it a fluke?!</i></font>

387
00:19:32,620 --> 00:19:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But his rhymes were too stiff!</i></font>

388
00:19:35,070 --> 00:19:37,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The lines were stiff too!</i></font>

389
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:40,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he experienced at this?!</i></font>

390
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, but...</i></font>

391
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, man!</font>

392
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">High schoolers should be at home 
doing homework!</font>

393
00:19:46,890 --> 00:19:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be the ones in trouble 
when your grades drop!</font>

394
00:19:49,910 --> 00:19:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Compared to you guys, 
that class monitor looks real smart!</font>

395
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:55,340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#15bdd0">Klutz</font></b></font></font>

396
00:19:56,970 --> 00:20:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We never even cared
 'bout our school's reputation!</i></font>

397
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:03,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Question how we live?
It don't matter to us.</i></font>

398
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They can go eat shit
with those stupid regulations!</i></font>

399
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You say our grades'll drop, 
but that ain't persuadin'!</i></font>

400
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All that waits at home 
is an annoying spiel.</i></font>

401
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This time with my crew's 
the only thing that's real.</i></font>

402
00:20:12,690 --> 00:20:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Better off ditchin' homework
 so I can hone my skills.</i></font>

403
00:20:15,190 --> 00:20:18,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A goody-two-shoes 
would never get this ideal.</i></font>

404
00:20:21,700 --> 00:20:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On the face of it, 
that sounded like a good rebuttal,</i></font>

405
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but if you ask me, it was a parade 
of stock phrases I've heard before.</i></font>

406
00:20:30,330 --> 00:20:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Though it'll still garner a good deal 
of support from the delinquents here.</i></font>

407
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! An honor student 
will never understand us!</font>

408
00:20:39,090 --> 00:20:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">School can eat shit!</font>

409
00:20:42,670 --> 00:20:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now, how will he fight back?!</i></font>

410
00:20:45,540 --> 00:20:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This determines the match!</i></font>

411
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The last eight bars!</i></font>

412
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say you don't care about</font>

413
00:20:52,450 --> 00:20:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your grades one bit,</font>

414
00:20:55,090 --> 00:20:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet here you are, 
showing off plenty of wit!</font>

415
00:20:57,990 --> 00:20:58,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?!</i></font>

416
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:00,110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<b><font color="#f3a3d2">Ba-dump...</font></b></font>

417
00:21:02,370 --> 00:21:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use that wisdom and cleverness 
your parents passed down,</font>

418
00:21:05,770 --> 00:21:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and you could turn 
your test scores right around!</font>

419
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to learn a thing or two
from your language unbound.</font>

420
00:21:12,290 --> 00:21:16,380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<b><font color="#f3a3d2">Ba-dump-dump...</font></b></font>

421
00:21:12,870 --> 00:21:16,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This honor student 
wants advice from me?!</i></font>

422
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what "my crew"
is supposed to mean,</font>

423
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:22,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm jealous that you're friends
 with so many teens.</font>

424
00:21:22,470 --> 00:21:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why not do things nice and proper?</font>

425
00:21:25,090 --> 00:21:26,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found a club and make it prosper!</font>

426
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:32,150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an7}<b><font color="#f3a3d2">Ba-dump
Ba-dump...</font></b></font>

427
00:21:28,470 --> 00:21:30,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A club?!</i></font>

428
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never even considered that.</i></font>

429
00:21:33,490 --> 00:21:34,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still...</i></font>

430
00:21:34,830 --> 00:21:39,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Outcasts like us in a club? A rap club?</i></font>

431
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do everything in my power 
to help you as well.</font>

432
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Work hard for our students.</font>

433
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the fundamental rule 
for class monitors!</font>

434
00:21:49,540 --> 00:21:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll speak to the school 
on your behalf as well.</font>

435
00:21:50,180 --> 00:21:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Way to go, class monitor!</font>

436
00:21:52,620 --> 00:21:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Thank you...</font>

437
00:21:53,040 --> 00:21:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You guys are the best!</font>

438
00:21:54,670 --> 00:21:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sakuradaimon!</font>

439
00:21:57,170 --> 00:21:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

440
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:00,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there.</font>

441
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

442
00:22:02,550 --> 00:22:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You remembered to show respect 
instead of just ending with a diss.</font>

443
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was very cool.</font>

444
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a great rap battle!</font>

445
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:15,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an9}<font size="11"><font color="#ffffff"><b>Translation: John Pickett
Timing: Mariana Martinez
Editing: Zachary Carlysle
Quality Control: SMR
Translation Check: Rei Miyasaka</b></font></font></font>

446
00:22:12,120 --> 00:22:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rap? Oh, sure, thanks.</font>

447
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'd love to ask for a match with you.</font>

448
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Would you someday...</font>

449
00:22:20,700 --> 00:22:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! Togo, you idiot!</font>

450
00:22:22,120 --> 00:22:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What are you doing wasting time here?!</font>

451
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You suddenly disappeared on me!</font>

452
00:22:27,170 --> 00:22:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in high school! You're too old 
to be getting lost, you klutz!</font>

453
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}N-No, Poem-san, you see...</font>

454
00:22:33,130 --> 00:22:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}P-Po-chan?</font>

455
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Geh?! Pa—Father?!</font>

456
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is your relationship 
with my daughter?!</font>

457
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Whoa!</font>

458
00:22:44,650 --> 00:22:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're friends!</font>

459
00:22:45,490 --> 00:22:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pa—Father, stop it!</font>

460
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He goes to my school!</font>

461
00:22:48,850 --> 00:22:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feast on this iron fist that'll leave 
weblike cracks in the asphalt!</font>

462
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen to me!</font>

